		<title>貓咪能分辨主人聲音嗎？從背後「3大」關鍵解密!</title>
		<link>https://firenews.com.tw/2025/09/14/%e8%b2%93%e5%92%aa%e8%83%bd%e5%88%86%e8%be%a8%e4%b8%bb%e4%ba%ba%e8%81%b2%e9%9f%b3%e5%97%8e%ef%bc%9f%e5%be%9e%e8%83%8c%e5%be%8c%e3%80%8c3%e5%a4%a7%e3%80%8d%e9%97%9c%e9%8d%b5%e8%a7%a3%e5%af%86/</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[火報 時事新聞]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Sun, 14 Sep 2025 07:09:14 +0000</pubDate>
